### Teacher routes

### Teacher dashboard
GET http://localhost:5173/teacher
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Teacher Students View
GET http://localhost:5173/teacher/students
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Teacher Lesson Create View
GET http://localhost:5173/teacher/lessons/new
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Teacher Lesson Edit View
GET http://localhost:5173/teacher/lessons/:lessonPublicId/edit
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Lesson Stats View
GET http://localhost:5173/teacher/lessons/:lessonPublicId/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Teacher Lesson Result View
GET http://localhost:5173/teacher/lessons/:lessonPublicId/students/:studentPublicId/result
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}




